patthana16.89:1.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ rūpāvacaraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho narūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.89:2.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ narūpāvacaraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā tīṇi …pe… avigate tīṇi.
